Finance::RawMaterialPrice version 0.01
=============================

Finance::RawMaterialPrice - To get the current gold and silver price

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::Simple

